Title: Vokera Excel i 30 20188734 combi boiler only pack
Description: Exclusively available to Wolseley customers, the Vokera Excel-i 30 combi boiler accepts a 20% hydrogen blend but is also suitable for operation via a methane-hydrogen blend to meet the requirements of imminent network switchovers. Fitted with a large bore stainless steel heat exchanger, this robust 30kW boiler is designed for reduced downtime, operating efficiently and reliably with regular servicing. Thanks to its simple, modern digital user interface, the Excel-i is easy to operate and commission with quick navigation through settings with no need to constantly refer back to the unit's instruction manual.

Title: Vokera Excel standard horizontal flue pack
Description: Vokera offer a wide range of flue systems that are able to meet the majority of applications. There are concentric flue systems and a parallel (twin) flue system that can be used in either horizontal or vertical configurations. All Vokera flue systems incorporate push-fit connections that are designed to enable a fast and simple method of installation.

Title: Vokera Vision Plus 25C boiler pack with flue
Description: Easy to install, the Vokera Vision Plus 25C combi boiler pack with flue offers siting flexibility through its smart compact design. Compatible with weather compensation sensors or with an OpenTherm control, such as BeSMART, this 25kW boiler already has an ErP A rating with the potential to improve efficiency for minimal environmental impact as well as even better comfort. User-friendly, the Vision Plus is designed with a backlit LCD display for intuitive operation while a three-mode, 7-day digital clock provides easy programming. Where an alternative control is installed, this internal clock is easily disabled.
